{"arkId":"cl010104324","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104324","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1725 - 1750","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1725,"endYear":1750,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Thiout, Antoine","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"vers 1694","place":"Jonvelle","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1767","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4775547"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6223","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ronde ; bo\u00eetier peint sur \u00e9mail orn\u00e9 d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne tir\u00e9e du roman d\u0027H\u00e9liodore, Amours de Th\u00e9ag\u00e8ne et Charicl\u00e9e, d\u0027apr\u00e8s une toile de Charles Poerson : le couple d\u0027amoureux se tient avec le pr\u00eatre Charicl\u00e8s et l\u0027\u00e9gyptienne Calasiris pr\u00e8s d\u0027une statue de Jupiter, un amour volant au-dessus d\u0027eux tenant deux couronnes de lauriers. Contre-\u00e9mail orn\u00e9 d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne de genre : un homme prom\u00e8ne deux chiens en laisse, un troisi\u00e8me chien poursuit deux canards. Sur le pourtour, quatre m\u00e9daillons contenant des paysages anim\u00e9s de sc\u00e8nes vari\u00e9s, s\u00e9par\u00e9s par des fleurs polychromes sur fond blanc. Lunettes en or grav\u00e9, charni\u00e8re moulur\u00e9e de filets. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains et arabes, brillants marquant les demi-heures, aiguilles reperc\u00e9es et enrichies de roses de diamant. Mouvement muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, d\u0027une fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eene, coq en argent grav\u00e9 et reperc\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris, de deux dragons et de feuilles d\u0027acanthe. Rosette de r\u00e9glage en argent marqu\u00e9e Avance-Retarde.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Thiout AParis","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,7","displayDimension":"6,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"5","displayDimension":"5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,8","displayDimension":"2,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jean-Charles Seguin (1857-1908), Paris. Legs, J.-Ch. Seguin, 1908.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Seguin, Jean-Charles","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1908","startYear":1908,"endYear":1908}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du L